<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Server Error - Chapter One</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-brown: #8B4513;
            --secondary-brown: #A67B5B;
            --light-brown: #D2B48C;
            --cream: #FFF8E7;
            --dark-brown: #3E2723;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            background-color: var(--cream);
            color: var(--dark-brown);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 4rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .error-title {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary-brown);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .error-subtitle {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--dark-brown);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .error-description {
            color: var(--secondary-brown);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary-brown);
            border-color: var(--primary-brown);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--dark-brown);
            border-color: var(--dark-brown);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: var(--light-brown);
            border-color: var(--light-brown);
            color: var(--dark-brown);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-brown);
            border-color: var(--secondary-brown);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .book-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--secondary-brown);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .loading-dots {
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .loading-dots:after {
            content: '...';
            animation: dots 1.5s steps(4, end) infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes dots {
            0%, 20% { content: ''; }
            40% { content: '.'; }
            60% { content: '..'; }
            80%, 100% { content: '...'; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container text-center">
        <div class="book-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="error-title">500</div>
        <h2 class="error-subtitle">Internal Server Error</h2>
        <p class="error-description">
            Oh no! It seems our library's magical book sorting system has encountered a glitch. 
            Our literary wizards are hard at work restoring order to the shelves.
        </p>
        <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="fw-bold">Restoring our collection<span class="loading-dots"></span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Return to Home
            </a>
            <button onclick="location.reload()" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
                <i class="fas fa-sync-alt me-2"></i>Try Again
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4">
            <small class="text-muted">
                <i class="fas fa-book me-2"></i>
                Even the greatest stories sometimes need an unexpected plot twist.
            </small>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.0/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>